text: Basic solution could be for the Problem statement :    Output = [] def Assignment(inputList):     temp = 90   #Selected using difference of first element of input and output.     for i in range(len(inputList)):         if(i==0):             Output.append(inputList[i]-temp)         else:             if(Output[-1]>(inputList[i]-temp)):                 temp-=10                 Output.append(inputList[i]-temp)             else:                 Output.append(inputList[i]-temp)     return Output  output = Assignment([1095,1094,1095]) print(output)     >>> [1005   ,   1014   ,  1015]
